 by the qualities of mind may like the story that demonstrates how mind ope=
rates, and one who is fascinated by the qualities of wisdom may like the st=
ory that demonstrates how wisdom operates. And so on. But this is just a ma=
tter of taste and subjective preference.=C2=A0*=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=
